Exercise: Write a fruitful function sum_to(n) that returns the sum of all integer numbers up to and including n.
So sum_to(10) would be 1+2+3...+10 which would return the value 55.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Solution: 

def sum_to(n):
    x = 0
    for i in range(n + 1):
        x = x + i
    return(x)

sum_to(10)
